description:
Interval timer The first rule of Zombieland; cardio. HIIT, high intensity interval timer, is a no frills timer for interval training routines, or anything you may need an interval timer for really. You may specify a number of seconds for each active period, a number of seconds for each rest period and, optionally, a number of seconds before the end of each rest period to warn of the upcoming active period giving you time to prepare.
  • No ads
  • No trackers
  • No permissions
  • Ultra simple interface
